1. Dependencies
1.1 FlvTool2 gem
1.2 ffmpeg
1.3 JRuby >= 1.0.3
1.4 activerecord-jdbc-adapter 0.7
1.5 derby or mysql

2. Deploy
2.1 rake db:backup:dump
2.2 change config/database.yml
2.3 rake testing
2.4 change config/war.rb
2.5 must be done after 2.2 testing!!! link upload-file-dir to the target
2.6 change the port in war_config.rb to 80
2.7 link mysql sock 